law.catch_line: Office of Occupations and Professions to provide assistance.
law.text: The Office of Occupations and Professions in the Public Protection Cabinet shall provide administrative aid to the board to assist it in the discharge of its duties.
law.history: Amended 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 24, sec. 1695, effective July 15, 2010. -- Amended 2009 Ky. Acts ch. 12, sec. 52, effective June 25, 2009. -- Amended 1992 Ky. Acts ch. 460, sec. 17, effective July 14, 1992. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 74, Art. VI, sec. 107(1). -- Created 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 48, sec. 17.
